      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A patient with diabetes and COPD developed postoperative urinary retention. Which of the following drugs can be used for short-term treatment to relieve the symptoms of this person?</span></span></span></p>",
